---
import SectionHead from './SectionHead.astro';
---
<section class="local sec wrap">
  <SectionHead eyebrow="Local Knowledge" title="We know Happy Valley plumbing, street by street." />
  <div class="local__cols">
    <p class="reveal" style="--rd:60ms">
      Happy Valley sits on the southern edge of Adelaide, and its housing tells a story. A lot
      of the area went up through the 1980s and 90s, which means we see plenty of ageing copper,
      tired galvanised runs and hot water units well past their best. The clay-heavy soil shifts
      with the seasons too, so slab cracks and root-invaded drains are part of the territory. We've
      worked on enough of these homes to know what to check first.
    </p>
    <p class="reveal" style="--rd:120ms">
      Being local means we're rarely far away. Whether you're near the Happy Valley Reservoir,
      up around Education Road, or closer to the shops on Kenihans Road, a burst pipe doesn't sit
      and wait. We carry the common parts on the van, so most jobs are sorted in a single visit.
      And because we live here, the work we do is work we'll stand behind when we see you at the
      footy or the bakery next week.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .local { background: var(--color-brand-bg); }
  .local__cols { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: clamp(28px,4vw,52px); }
  .local__cols p { font-family: var(--font-body); font-size: 15.5px; line-height: 1.75; color: var(--color-brand-muted); margin: 0; }
  @media (max-width: 760px) { .local__cols { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }
</style>
